    "abstract": {
      "description": "These are the DELPHI online logbooks. There used to be three people on shift during data taking, having different roles. Available logs books are these of the shift leader, the data aquisition logs, the slow control maestro and the quality checker. In addition, for later years, logbooks from the HPC detector shifter are preserved and available here."
    },
